    the context is canceled. However, in reality, tests sometimes take
    a while to return, e.g. if it tries to copy large files in deferred
    function calls. And when it happens tests may not report useful error
    messages.
    
    Currently only 3 seconds is allowed between a test timeout and test
    bundle abort. This patch increases it to 30 seconds.
    
