    This change adds support of declaring build artifacts as external
    data files in the following JSON format:
    
    {
      "type": "artifact",
      "name": "license_credits.html"
    }
    
    If this JSON is found as *.external in data/ directory, the file at
    
      gs://chromeos-image-archive/$BUILDER_PATH/license_credits.html
    
    is downloaded to the DUT, where $BUILDER_PATH is a string found as
    CHROMEOS_RELEASE_BUILDER_PATH in /etc/lsb-release. Afterwards,
    those files can be accessible in tests with s.DataPath just like
    other static external data files.
    
